c: 60
v: 1
t: "A wid iumnen! Ur ddukulet d icenga W akked icenga nnwen. Teram ten d iﾃｪbiben, u nitni nekﾃｴen ayen id iusan, $uﾃｴwen, n tidep. ﾃ暗ｨﾃｩaﾃ｢n Amazan, ﾃｩﾃｩaﾃ｢n kwen, imi tumnem s ﾃ貌bbi, Mass nnwen. Ma teff$em a ppenna$em deg ubrid iW, u tepnadim ﾃｴﾃｴva W, day a ten terrem, s tuffra, d iﾃｪbiben? Nek, Ife$ akw akken ﾃｨﾃｴi$, ayen teffrem akked wayen tennam. Win, segwen, ixedmen akka, innetlaf seg ubrid umﾃ｢in"